data.text:
VIA Entertainment has everything you need for a family fun day! We proudly offer ultra-modern bowling lanes, an expansive arcade, an indoor go-kart track, Virtual Reality games, a sports bar and grill, event facilities, laser tag, escape room, black-light mini golf, and axe throwing.

We are conveniently located at the back of Lake Square Mall.
